---
import Container from "./Container.astro";

---
<div id="quick" class="mx-auto">
    <Container>
        <div>
            <div class="lg:w-3/4 mx-auto">
                <div class="my-8 flex flex-row place-content-start">
                    <div>
                        <img
                        src="/images/icons/fast-time.png"
                        class="w-12 fill-white"
                        width="512"
                        height="512"
                        alt="stopwatch illustration"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white md:text-4xl pl-2">Quick Coaching</h2></div>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">With Quick Coaching, you get a preset number of sessions on specific topics for a flat fee.
                    It's the most cost-effective form of coaching. 
                    I'll walk you through the most common considerations, processes, best practices, and pitfalls and answer questions related to your use case.
                </p>
                <p class="pt-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                    I'll also provide homework and templates to generate documents and plans to keep you organized and on-track.
                </p>
                <p class="pt-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                    This Quick Coaching package is <span class="text-primary dark:text-sky-300">two one-hour sessions</span> offering guidance on these topics:
                </p>
                
                <div class="lg:w-3/4 mx-auto">
                    <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Getting Buy-In</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">You'll leave this session with actionable strategies to generate internal enthusiasm, seek feedback, and pivot quickly.
                        Guided homework will help you identify key stakeholders and champions and the key communication channels you'll use.
                    </p>
                    <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Communication & Engagement</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        You'll leave this session with a list of the key communication moments and methods you'll need for engaging your stakeholders and cultivating champions,
                        whether that's asking for contributions, announcing your project launch to end-users, or talking to your higher-ups or colleagues about what you're doing.
                        Guided homework includes templates to help you craft your communications.
                    </p>
                    <h3 class="my-8 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Cost: <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">$400 USD</span></h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        <div>
    </Container>
</div>